SAtl_Climate_MSE_Results

Cassidy Peterson

2/28/2023

Background

Here are the results from a South Atlantic MSE exercise testing the behavior of model-based versus empirical MPs for black sea bass (BSB), vermilion snapper (VS), and red porgy (RP) using the openMSE software (Blue Matter Science).

Below are the results for BSB.
